# ACTIS Maintainers

**Steward:** The ACTIS specification is maintained by the actis-spec organization (https://github.com/actis-spec). The repository actis-spec/actis is the canonical source.

**Current maintainer identification:** For named maintainers and contact, see the repository description on GitHub or the repository README. This file MUST be kept accurate so that evaluators and implementers know who maintains ACTIS.

**Governance:** Versioning, change process, and transition to a multi-maintainer model are defined in GOVERNANCE.md.
